title: Portillo the Wiener Dog vs. Chloe the Dumb Cat
description:
There's been a fight brewing in the PlayStation Home for a while now -- Portillo the wiener dog against Chloe the dumb cat. For months, each has won small battles in the great war. Today, one walks away the undisputed winner.

Video courtesy of the Steimer News Network.

transcript_chunks.text: Yeah, I know it. Open your hands. And go. Bark, bark!
